message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with speech processing and separation. Other likely categories could be cs.CL (computational linguistics) as the paper deals with speech processing, cs.LG (machine learning) as the paper proposes a deep learning system, cs.SI (signal processing) as the paper deals with audio signal processing, and cs.SY (systems and control) as the paper proposes a system for real-time speech separation.
